reviewText: If you're a Family Guy geek and you love the humor of this cartoon sitcom you have got to get this collection. I have cable with over 150 channels but sometimes there is just nothing on. So, I simply slip a disc into my DVD player and viola, Compare the cost of this entire set to buying each season separately and you save a bundle.
I love the raunchy humor.  One of the funniest shows ever.

Great show, but if you are looking at this you probably agree.

The problem with the product is the description says that it includes seasons 1-12. Volumes 1-12 only covers seasins 1-11.  The seasons are broken up oddly over the volumes.
